**LIX readability score calculator:**

https://herramientas.educaLAB.es/es/herramientas/lix

**Analysis:**

* Number of words (excluding prepositions): 141
* Number of sentences: 14
* Average sentence length: 141 / 14 = 10.1
* Number of words longer than 6 letters: 65

**Formula:**

LIX = (Average sentence length / 100) + (Number of words longer than 6 letters / Number of words) * 100

**Calculation:**

LIX = ((10.1 / 100) + ((65 / 141) * 100)) = **40.1**

**Result:**

LIX=40.1